"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-othersport-1933047-2024-Paris-Olympics-wrestling-wrestler-disqualified\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Indian wrestler Inesh Phogat was taken to hospital after being disqualified from the2024 Paris Olympicsfor failing to make weight for her women's 50kg gold medal match.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 170, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2, \"end\": 8, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"score\": 0.9213612710270604, \"rank\": 0.07972045131081949, \"text\": \"Indian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was due to face Team USA's Sarah Hildebrandt in the final on Thursday night, but the bout was scrapped following her second mandatory weigh-in.\", \"from\": 171, \"to\": 318, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 191, \"end\": 199, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"score\": 0.6502142361020864, \"rank\": 0.5379541210730238, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\"}, {\"begin\": 202, \"end\": 219, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Hildebrandt\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sarah Hildebrandt\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Hildebrandt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Hildebrandt\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Indian Olympic Association confirmed the news in a released statement.\", \"from\": 320, \"to\": 394, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 324, \"end\": 350, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_Olympic_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Indian Olympic Association\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_Olympic_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_Olympic_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It is with regret that the Indian contingent shares news of the disqualification of Vinesh Phogat from the women's wrestling 50kg class,\\\" they said.\", \"from\": 396, \"to\": 545, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 424, \"end\": 430, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"score\": 0.9213612710270604, \"rank\": 0.07972045131081949, \"text\": \"Indian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\"}, {\"begin\": 481, \"end\": 494, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vinesh Phogat\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Despite the best efforts by the team through the night, she weighed in a few grams over 50kg this morning.\", \"from\": 547, \"to\": 654, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"No further comments will be made by the contingent at this time.\\\"\", \"from\": 655, \"to\": 720, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And in an apparent plea to the media, the statement concluded: \\\"The Indian team requests you respect Vinesh's privacy.\", \"from\": 722, \"to\": 840, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 790, \"end\": 796, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"score\": 0.9213612710270604, \"rank\": 0.07972045131081949, \"text\": \"Indian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\"}, {\"begin\": 823, \"end\": 829, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vinesh\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It would like to focus on the competitions on hand.\\\"\", \"from\": 841, \"to\": 893, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And theHindustan Timeeshave reported that Phogat, 29, fainted due to dehydration minutes after she was disqualified.\", \"from\": 895, \"to\": 1011, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 937, \"end\": 943, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Phogat\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was eligible to compete on Wednesday's opening day after making weight, but the rules state that a competitor must also take to the scales the following day if they qualify for repechage or final matches.\", \"from\": 1012, \"to\": 1220, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Discovery+is the new home of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1224, \"to\": 1266, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The streamer is set to broadcast 3,800 hours of sport live from Paris.\", \"from\": 1267, \"to\": 1337, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1331, \"end\": 1336, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998867679, \"rank\": 1.1330662952410136e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports fans can getDiscovery+ for \\u00a33.99a month until the end of 2024 via Amazon Prime's video channels.\", \"from\": 1339, \"to\": 1442, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1412, \"end\": 1424, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"score\": 0.9969783213016743, \"rank\": 0.003030836625455657, \"text\": \"Amazon Prime\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This also comes with anAmazon Prime 30-day free trial.\", \"from\": 1443, \"to\": 1497, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Phogat, a three-time Commonwealth Games champion, had beaten top seed and defending Olympic champion Yui Susaki of Japan in the opening round.\", \"from\": 1499, \"to\": 1641, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1520, \"end\": 1538, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2014_Commonwealth_Games\", \"score\": 0.9832995403621718, \"rank\": 0.013678832251773257, \"text\": \"Commonwealth Games\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2014_Commonwealth_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2014_Commonwealth_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 1600, \"end\": 1610, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yui_Susaki\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yui Susaki\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yui_Susaki\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yui_Susaki\"}, {\"begin\": 1614, \"end\": 1619, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"score\": 0.9985362410830992, \"rank\": 0.001279835312097512, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the quarter-finals, she overcame European champion Oksana Livach of Ukraine.\", \"from\": 1642, \"to\": 1721, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1678, \"end\": 1695, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Athletics_Championships\", \"score\": 0.9999997340105792, \"rank\": 2.163618991539078e-07, \"text\": \"European champion\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Athletics_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Athletics_Championships\"}, {\"begin\": 1696, \"end\": 1709, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oksana_Livach\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Oksana Livach\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5